e who allow blasphemy over their shrines like this, such a people lose a right to be respected by their still believing neighbors\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://faith.pravda.ru/faithculture/10-11-2018/1134147-last_temptation-0/|title=\u041f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u043d\u0435\u0435 \u0438\u0441\u043a\u0443\u0448\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u0425\u0440\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0430\" - \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u0430\u044f \u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0447\u043a\u0430 \u0432 \u0447\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0435 \u0441\u043e\u0431\u043b\u0430\u0437\u043d\u043e\u0432|trans-title=\"The Last Temptation of Christ\" - first in a row of temptations|publisher=[[Pravda.ru]]|date=November 10, 2018|accessdate=November 19, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116042238/https://faith.pravda.ru/faithculture/10-11-2018/1134147-last_temptation-0/|archivedate=November 16, 2018|quote=And the truth is - if you already begin to blaspheme with your very artistic pseudonym on the topic of the name of the Mother of God - then why not end up with anger at her Divine Son?|language=Russian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vesti.ru/doc.html?id=116292|title=\u0410\u043d\u0434\u0440\u0435\u0439 \u041a\u0443\u0440\u0430\u0435\u0432: \u043d\u0435\u043b\u044c\u0437\u044f \u0437\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0431\u0430\u0442\u044b\u0432\u0430\u0442\u044c \u0434\u0435\u043d\u044c\u0433\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u0447\u0443\u0436\u043e\u0439 \u0431\u043e\u043b\u0438|trans-title=[[Andrey Kuraev]]: you cannot make money from someone else's pain|publisher=[[Vesti.Ru]]|date=September 12, 2006|accessdate=August 29, 2018|language=Russian|quote=The name, which for billions of people on the earth and in the history of the earth is perceived as a symbol of utmost purity - the Madonna, Virgin Mary, Mother of God - has become the stage nickname of a porn star}}</ref> ''[[Rolling Stone]] Russia'' on ''[[Like a Prayer (song)|Like a Prayer]]'': \"In the title gospel-style song Louise Ciccone completely changes her st