l-phenomenon|title=\u042d\u0444\u0444\u0435\u043a\u0442 \u041c\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0435\u043b\u044b. \u0418\u0441\u043a\u0443\u0441\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0441\u0435\u043d\u0441\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f \u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0440\u0435\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u0444\u0435\u043d\u043e\u043c\u0435\u043d?|trans-title=Mandela effect. Artificial sensation or real phenomenon? |publisher=\u041d\u0430\u0443\u0447\u043d\u043e-\u043f\u043e\u043f\u0443\u043b\u044f\u0440\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u0436\u0443\u0440\u043d\u0430\u043b \u041f\u0441\u0438\u0445\u043e\u041f\u043e\u0438\u0441\u043a|quote=A widely known method for the diagnosis of paramnesia under the name \"Diz - Rodiger - McDermott Paradigm\" demonstrates how false memories can easily appear if there is a semantic basis for this in the past|date=June 4, 2018|accessdate=May 8, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508094348/https://psychosearch.ru/teoriya/determin/591-the-mandela-effect-an-artificial-sensation-or-a-real-phenomenon|archivedate=May 8, 2019|language=Russian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.meltingreality.com/effect-mandeli-angl-primer-bible-films/|title=\u042d\u0424\u0424\u0415\u041a\u0422 \u041c\u0410\u041d\u0414\u0415\u041b\u042b \u2014 \u0410\u041d\u0413\u041b\u041e\u042f\u0417\u042b\u0427\u041d\u042b\u0415 \u0412\u0418\u0414\u0415\u041e, \u0424\u0410\u041a\u0422\u042b, \u041e\u0411\u0421\u0423\u0416\u0414\u0415\u041d\u0418\u0415|trans-title=Mandela Effect - English videos, facts, discussion|publisher=\u00ab\u0426\u0438\u0444\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u044f \u0412\u0441\u0435\u043b\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0430\u044f\u00bb|accessdate=August 8, 2018|quote=It turns out that \u201cMadonna\u201d is not the creative pseudonym of the singer, whose name was Maria Louise Ciccone ... Now, it turns out, from childhood she was Madonna Louise Ciccone|archivedate=January 17, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117090507/http://www.meltingreality.com/effect-mandeli-angl-primer-bible-films/|url-status=live|language=Russian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://wikirank.net/ru/%D0%9C%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(%D0%BF%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%86%D0%B0)|title=Madonna (entertainer) - Russian is the second most popular language of the article with 11.8197%|publisher=[[Wikirank.net|Wikirank]]|accessdate=September 16, 2019}}</ref> In 2019, deputy Milonov spoke on a subject considering a possible law about banning foreign artists from political statements: \"For example, apart from her concert program an outstanding American singer Madonna was expressing her political preferences and was trying to conduct a political agitation regarding the criticism of Russian legislation\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ria.ru/20190803/1557133719.html|title=\u041c\u0438\u043b\u043e\u043d\u043e\u0432 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u043b\u043e\u0436\u0438\u043b \u0440\u0430\u0437\u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0430\u0442\u044c \u0441\u043f\u0435\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0435 \u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u043b\u0430 \u0434\u043b\u044f Rammstein \u0438 \u041c\u0430\u0434\u043e\u043d\u043d\u044b|trans-title=Milonov proposed to develop special rules for Rammstein and Madonna|publisher=[[RIA Novosti]]|date=August 3, 2019|accessdate=September 6, 2019|language =Russian}}</ref> According to [[YouGov]], in Russia the singer-songwriter is regularly voted as one of the ten most admirable women, e. g. she had 6,28% and 6th overall place in 2019, with first woman in space [[Valentina Tereshkova]] on a 1st place.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://yougov.co.uk/topics/international/articles-reports/2015/01/30/most-admired-2015|title=World's most admired 2015: Angelina Jolie and Bill Gates|publisher=[[YouGov]]|date=January 1, 2015|accessdate=January 11, 2019|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/75LjESQWW?url=https://yougov.co.uk/topics/international/articles-reports/2015/01/30/most-admired-2015|archivedate=January 11, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://y