\u0438\u0446\u0435\u043c\u0435\u0440\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0445\u043e\u0439 \u0438 \u0434\u0443\u0440\u043e\u0439|trans-title=Milonov called Madonna a hypocritical old woman and stupid|publisher=Gazeta Spb|date=August 8, 2015|accessdate=December 5, 2019}}</ref>\n \n[[File:Madonna - Logo 2014.png|33%|frame|left|Madonna's logo in 2014 with \"Madonia\" (Latin for \"Madonnaland\"<ref group=\"note\">In 2015, [[Texas University Press]] hired Russian-born Madonna skepticist [[Alina Simone]] to write a book ''[[Madonnaland]]''. For an exapmle of level of Alina's research, she calls Madonna's ballet teacher Christopher Flinn a \"black gay\".</ref>) word using Russian \"\u0438\" for \"i\" letter. One of the key points of Russian history, a subject that fancied Madonnaa since her childhood years,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.ie/entertainment/music/live-to-tell-an-exclusive-interview-with-madonna-31074485.html|title=Live to tell... an exclusive interview with Madonna|publisher=Independent (Ireland)|date=March 23, 2015|accessdate=December 11, 2019}}</ref> is the denial of theory that the pre-country was defeated in 9th century and renamed into Rus' after its conqueror, Danish Viking [[Rorik of Dorestad##Rorik and Rurik|Rurik]] from [[Scylding]] dynasty.<ref group=note>Meanwhile, neighboring [[Finns]], [[Estonians]], and [[Latvians]] don't recognize the renaming of Rurik occupied territory and peoples to this day, ''[[Russia]]'' is officially called {{lang-fi|Ven\u00e4j\u00e4}}, {{lang-et|Venemaa}}, and {{lang-lv|Krievija}} (see also Eastern [[Galindians]], Baltic people near Moscow completely assimilated as \"Pravoslavnye\" (Russian translation of Greek word \"Orthodox\" \u2014 {{lang-rus|\u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0430\u0432\u043d\u044b\u0435|pravoslavnye}}, is spelled and pronounced very similar to the word \"Proto-Slavic\" \u2014 {{lang-rus|\u043f\u0440\u0430\u0441\u043b\u0430\u0432\u044f\u043d\u0435|praslavyane}}). The term \"Orthodox\" was perceived as an ethnical identity in [[Russian Empire]], and after collapse of a Soviet Union people were encouraged to list themselves as \"Orthodox\" in a polls, based on a fact of their origin from Russian peasants (Russian word \"peasant\" ({{lang-rus|\u043a\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0442\u044c\u044f\u043d\u0438\u043d|krest'yanin}}) is a term delivered from \"Christian\" ({{lang-rus|\u0445\u0440\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0430\u043d\u0438\u043d|christianin}})). Thus, Madonna's [[Harper's Bazaar]] quote about wearing a scarf \"like a Russian peasant\" can also be translated as \"like an Orthodox Christian\".</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.harpersbazaar.com/celebrity/latest/news/a1095/madonna-interview-1113/|title=Madonna's Back|publisher=[[Harper's Bazaar]]|date=October 4, 2013|accessdate=March 4, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109174549/https://www.harpersbazaar.com/celebrity/latest/news/a1095/madonna-interview-1113/|archivedate=January 9, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|quote=Nobody could ever conquer Russia|title=\u0417\u0430\u0447\u0435\u043c \u041c\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0432\u0430 \u043e\u0442\u043c\u0435\u043d\u044f\u0435\u0442 \u043c\u043e\u043d\u0433\u043e\u043b\u043e-\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0430\u0440\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0435 \u0438\u0433\u043e?|trans-title=Why is Moscow denying the Mongol-Tatar yoke?|url=https://www.obozrevatel.com/abroad/zachem-moskva-otmenyaet-mongolo-tatarskoe-igo.htm|publisher=Obozrevatel.com (Ukraine)|date=January 23, 2018|accessdate=December 11, 2019|language=Russian}}.</ref><ref>{{cite web|quote=Therefore, when they ask me: \"What is Russian?\" - I do not know. I just say, they're similar to the Irish, in my opinion. \u201cTo the Irish ??\u201d - I say \"Yes\". Because the ups and downs of mood are typical - one. They like to drink - two. They like to fight - three. They like to have friends - four. Literary talent - five. All the great English writers are actually Irish. Almost all of them. And one more thing: there were a lot of victims. After all, the Irish suffered 800 years from the British! And the Russians - from the Tatars. And then, not only from the Tatars. And suffering adds something|url=https://pozneronline.ru/2018/07/21824/|title=\u0412\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0438\u043c\u0438\u0440 \u041f\u043e\u0437\u043d\u0435\u0440 \u043e \u0440\u0443\u0441\u0441\u043a\u043e\u043c \u0447\u0435\u043b\u043e\u0432\u0435\u043a\u0435|trans-title=[[Vladimir Pozner Jr.|Vladimir Pozner]] about Russian personality|date=July 16, 2018|accessdate=December 12, 2019|language=Russian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.todayfm.com/muireann-oconnell/ten-times-madonna-proved-she-is-actually-irish-329889|title=Ten Times Madonna Proved She Is Actually Irish|publisher=Today FM|date=August 16, 2018|accessdate=December 12, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2015/dec/28/origins-of-the-irish-down-to-mass-migration-ancient-dna-confirms|title=Irish DNA originated in Middle East and eastern Europe|publisher=Guardian|date=December 28, 2015|accessdate=December 12, 2019}}</ref> By coincidence, Madonna was using [[Cyrillic script|Cyrillyc letters]] as a decoration for her first performance with \"[[Everybody (Madonna song)|Everybody]]\" in the Danceteria, and her use of {{runic|\u16d7}} ([[Mannaz]]) [[Runic alphabet]] letter, as [[Madame X Tour]] logo.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ttJBJTcnroc|title=Everybody - live at the Danceteria|publisher=Official Madonna YouTube}}</ref> According to Chinese ''[[Sina Corp|Sina]]'', Europeans have historically perceived Russians as Asian people with [[Mongol]]ian blood.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://inosmi.ru/social/20190922/245855920.html|title=Sina (\u041a\u0438\u0442\u0430\u0439): \u0438\u0441\u043f\u043e\u043a\u043e\u043d \u0432\u0435\u043a\u043e\u0432 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u044f \u2013 \u0435\u0432\u0440\u043e\u043f\u0435\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430\u044f \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430, \u04