ccess in a country because [[MTV (Russian TV channel)|MTV]] was launched in Russia just in 1998.<ref group=\"note\">[[Lyubov Orlova]] performed the most famous \"[[Bayan (accordion)|bayan]] playing\" female dance on \"{{ill|Fighting Film Colletcion #4|ru|\u0411\u043e\u0435\u0432\u043e\u0439 \u043a\u0438\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0431\u043e\u0440\u043d\u0438\u043a \u2116 4}}\" (1941), a series of motivational propaganda movies during [[World War II]] [https://youtube.com/watch?v=1i8UdkQwsC8&start=3367 ]. An official biography claims her distant [[House of Rurik]] ancestry [http://www.lubov-orlova.ru/bio/detstvo.html ].</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mycityua.com/articles/people/2009/12/21/064447.html|title=\u0422\u0418\u041c\u0423\u0420 \u0411\u0415\u041a\u041c\u0410\u041c\u0411\u0415\u0422\u041e\u0412: \"\u0425\u041e\u0427\u0423 \u0421\u041d\u042f\u0422\u042c \u0424\u0418\u041b\u042c\u041c \u041f\u0420\u041e \u041b\u042e\u0411\u041e\u0412\u042c \u041e\u0420\u041b\u041e\u0412\u0423 \u0421 \u041c\u0410\u0414\u041e\u041d\u041d\u041e\u0419 \u0412 \u0413\u041b\u0410\u0412\u041d\u041e\u0419 \u0420\u041e\u041b\u0418\"|trans-title=[[Timur Bekmambetov]]: \"I would like to make a movie about [[Lyubov Orlova]] with Madonna. But it's just a dream\"|publisher=MyCityUA.com|date=December 21, 2009|archiveurl=https://www.liveinternet.ru/community/in_bed_with_madonna/post117094479/|archivedate=December 21, 2009| quote= Madonna could play Orlova very well. But for now, these are just fantasies|language=Russian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://likeness.ru/blog/tag/%D0%BC%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BD%D0%B0/|title=\u041c\u0430\u0434\u043e\u043d\u043d\u0430|trans-title=Madonna|publisher=Likeness.ru - fun similiarities|quote= TOP 4 Madonna likenesses: 1. Johnny Depp as [[Alice in Wonderland (2010 film)|Mad Hatter]] - 864 votes; 2. [[Sasha Gradiva|Sasha]] - 178 votes; 3. [[:ru:\u0420\u0443\u0431\u0446\u043e\u0432\u0430, \u0412\u0430\u043b\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u041f\u0430\u0432\